pr_body:
I'd like to return JSON error responses in the format of
```json
{
    "message": "Some error message"
}
```
instead of

```json
{
    "msg": "Some error message"
}
```

This PR allows that to be customized via the `JWT_ERROR_MESSAGE_KEY` configuration option.

